edu.snu.rixk.model

Class GameState

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.snu.rixk.model.GameState

  • public class GameState
extends java.lang.Object
    This is Model object holds the major state of the game. This includes the current Player objects, the RixkMap, the current Phase of the game, the acting Player, the order of play, the game statistics, and the two sets of Dice.
